    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and finely slice your <strong>shallot[s] </strong>and peel and grate (don't chop!) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Cut your <strong>chicken breast portion[s] </strong>in half, lengthways</p><p>Add the <strong>sliced shallot </strong>to a large bowl with the <strong>halved</strong> <strong>chicken</strong>, your <strong>cumin seeds</strong>, <strong>ground</strong> <strong>smoked paprika</strong>, <strong>red wine vinegar</strong>, <strong>half </strong>the<strong> grated garlic </strong>(save the rest for later!)<strong> </strong>and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
