    {
      "instruction": "<p>Give everything a good mix up and season with a very generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper </strong>– this is your <strong>marinated chicken</strong></p><p>Thread the <strong>marinated chicken</strong> and <strong>sliced shallot </strong>onto the <strong>soaked</strong> <strong>skewer[s]</strong> in a snake-like fashion – this is your <strong>marinated chicken skewer[s]</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1679394937423-x200.jpg",
