    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice your <strong>tomato[es]</strong> into rounds</p><p>Strip your <strong>mint</strong> <strong>leaves</strong> from their stems and chop them roughly, discard the stems</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
