            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>To build your sandwich, fill the <strong>crusty</strong> <strong>ciabatta</strong> with the <strong>sliced</strong> <strong>chicken breast souvlaki</strong>,<strong> </strong>a<strong> </strong>dollop of<strong> tzatziki</strong>, a couple of <strong>herby fries </strong>and a<strong> tomato round </strong>– this is your <strong>chicken breast souvlaki sandwich</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>remaining herby fries</strong> to the side with the <strong>remaining chicken breast souvlaki skewer</strong>, <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>tomato rounds</strong>,<strong> sliced cucumber</strong> and<strong> reserved chopped mint</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
